entry.title: yicm/CMakeCppProjectTemplate
entry.summary: This project aims to quickly launch a C/C++ project, which can build libraries and binary files. The project comes with basic modules such as thread pool, unit test, logger, and configuration reading module. It uses the CMake build system to make it easier for us to develop C/C++ projects.
